articles.title: Stephen Curry wins American Century Championship with eagle on 18 - ESPN - ESPN
articles.description: Warriors star Stephen Curry holed an eagle putt on 18 to win the American Century Championship over Mardy Fish on Sunday.
articles.content:
Jul 16, 2023, 09:02 PM ET
Golden State Warriors star Stephen Curry rolled in a long eagle putt on the final hole to win the American Century Championship on Sunday in Stateline, Nevada.
